WEBVTT

00:02.569 --> 00:04.002
Every mall has a Hoffritz in it.

00:05.489 --> 00:08.322
That's got to be a scary place
to work. I don't know how you feel.

00:08.489 --> 00:10.445
Do you want to stand there
having people going:

00:10.609 --> 00:13.043
"I need knives.
I need more knives.

00:13.209 --> 00:15.120
Do you have any bigger knives?

00:15.289 --> 00:17.757
I'd like a bigger knife.
A big, long, sharp knife.

00:17.929 --> 00:20.489
That's what I'm in the market for.
I like them really sharp.

00:20.649 --> 00:22.480
Do you have one
with hooks and gouges...

00:22.649 --> 00:25.288
...and blades
that are kind of serrated?

00:25.449 --> 00:27.917
That's the kind of knife
I'm looking for.

00:28.209 --> 00:30.723
I need one I can throw.
I need one I can hack away with.

00:30.889 --> 00:33.039
Do you have anything like that?"

